flowchart LR
    A[User] -->|Requests Access| B[Google Auth Server]
    B -->|Redirects to||Consent Page| C[User Consent]
    C -->|Grants Consent| D[Authorization Code]
    D -->|Sends Code||to Google Auth Server| B
    B -->|Exchanges Code||for Access Token| E[Access Token]
    E -->|Sends Token||to Client App| F[Client App]
    F -->|Uses Token||for API Requests| G[Google API]
    A -->|Uses API||with Token| G